{"tid":825594,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭好應該辭職！","createTime":"2018-09-17T16:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T08:20:47.000Z","uid":13448,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"824803d3fa67b00433a9662aca5a1936e5b1e657","tid":825594,"uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"今日身為特首既林鄭好應該辭退職業<br />\n理應帶領市民 但就望住市民死<br />\n如果身為特首既佢呼籲叫人今日唔好返出/出外有危險<br />\n今日都唔會有咁多死傷者出現<br />\n咩叫自行決定？比你屌 你屌唔屌既道理？<br />\n係天災定人禍？無叫市民小心風後既危險性 <br />\n的確政府無能力決定僱主開唔開工<br />\n但以佢身分係可以建議僱主/大眾點做 <br />\n如果僱主睇到政府立場係唔建議返工同外出<br />\n咁僱主硬要推人返工就僱主責任 <br />\n但林鄭就無做好領導工作 好應該就主流民意自己辭職<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/000716_f0e2a598a44bcd266e5b43d424d8a3a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F000716_f0e2a598a44bcd266e5b43d424d8a3a6.png&h=2182cc44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e5a20e091b8ebcb3bc6eb8a9a648c8049c8b9fe","tid":825594,"uid":37666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:16:10.000Z","msg":"切腹啦林鄭個撚樣<br />\n離撚哂地<br />\n你唔出街睇新聞都見到成地樹啦，地鐵都失靈啦<br />\n個撚樣真係為咗搵錢唔理我地有冇事架喎！根本唔關心啲小市民死傷"},{"pid":"9354d38c0b90f196109aa5a45aedbb111080a93d","tid":825594,"uid":54992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥食屎啦"},{"pid":"03425c341e446f4cda211d0295736422d757738a","tid":825594,"uid":13448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:44:12.000Z","msg":"山竹只係天災<br />\n林鄭絕對係人禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d672c305fd31811ade0ccb91224a5a3dee52f67","tid":825594,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"林鄭應一死以謝天下"},{"pid":"cb0b1f00720f87ce557b958ae2bd71317fe84815","tid":825594,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T00:46:49.000Z","msg":"連登捉五毛大隊長出咗呢個po <br />\n<br />\n嗱!林鄭你就衰撚左架啦，<span style=\"color: red;\">畀多次機會你</span>，明天星期二補假一天，包你民望上到80。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bBnEAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bBnEAS</a>"},{"pid":"5387c460521e4e6d1c7e163ac34c9c767194ac59","tid":825594,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"佢既出現並唔係管治, 係言聽計從.  Full Stop."},{"pid":"1aea879ea47ef2705d80547c47d5527e816cf755","tid":825594,"uid":211145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"你做特首好冇？"}]}